<br />\n係咪就畢業果陣報名就得</blockquote><br />\n咁唔好做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c899b05913aac6fc96338c610990402df143addb","tid":329357,"uid":930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:06:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問咁多位<br />\n黎緊大學 最後一年 非工程degree<br />\n想入行做飛機工程<br />\n<br />\n個人有興趣係依方面發展<br />\n係咪就畢業果陣報名就得</blockquote><br />\n咁唔好做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解 其實我都考慮過好多野<br />\n個人鍾意落手落腳做，多過坐寫字樓<br />\n有朋友做緊 聽佢講我都幾有興趣"},{"pid":"05849c13dabbd891e5392dccde93e30072d8c0cf","tid":329357,"uid":57069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T02:33:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ps  拎返個5人足球冠軍同7人足球老年隊亞軍先走</blockquote><br />\n射波王？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/22/103330_866309e85183e22e4aeb212ca24a2a07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F22%2F103330_866309e85183e22e4aeb212ca24a2a07.jpg&h=6c252c49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b34a93d7a9904d6b025ccc351420697ce560db20","tid":329357,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曾經做過heaco LM，轉左行做IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 師兄做左幾耐？<br />\nIT工時長唔長過LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n而家舒服好多，果陣LM返12.5鐘仲未計車程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家朝九晚五<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe960ab2aff0049d1bfddc8438f7756e840d7229","tid":329357,"uid":124743,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:17:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問咁多位<br />\n黎緊大學 最後一年 非工程degree<br />\n想入行做飛機工程<br />\n<br />\n個人有興趣係依方面發展<br />\n係咪就畢業果陣報名就得</blockquote><br />\n咁唔好做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解 其實我都考慮過好多野<br />\n個人鍾意落手落腳做，多過坐寫字樓<br />\n有朋友做緊 聽佢講我都幾有興趣</blockquote><br />\n你要考左CAD 幾科modules先<br />\nApply AELT<br />\naircraft engineering licensed trainee<br />\n你只要within個program期間, 考曬成個CAD B牌<br />\n畢業就係做Dual Function ( Inspector 收貨 出蛇）<br />\n但HAECO迫你加班<br />\n唔加班底薪同出面一樣<br />\n加左就多啲<br />\n返BM 基本工時 0800-1800 count你9.5working hours 1700後當加班 工時x1.5<br />\n返朝8放晚8就出12.5個working hours錢<br />\n中間一個鐘食飯無錢<br />\n全日有兩個tea break, 每個15分鐘<br />\n但我地有前三後三（前15分同後15分鐘）<br />\n收工等放break <br />\n放完慢慢行返飛機開工<br />\n公司風氣，6點後自己「收工」<br />\n有人食煙吹水、食飯、玩啤牌、溫書<br />\n小弟就係加班去溫書<br />\n比埋錢你溫書算係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（小弟依家做緊，覺得HAECO算唔錯，自由同專業，但要考返個牌先有得撈，升工程師/dual function。唔考都得，靠經驗同人事做返12-3年以上，會升到supervisor, 底薪20000幾，每日收8點就30000幾40000）"},{"pid":"bb84a1ffb8d09bab73b0cdac6f5bb97080fe062d","tid":329357,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:03:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n前LM tech1</blockquote><br />\n去左邊度發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔做港機！咪做港鐵囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98d2e6306dba9072eb3ebfa6371e200118f4a93","tid":329357,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問咁多位<br />\n黎緊大學 最後一年 非工程degree<br />\n想入行做飛機工程<br />\n<br />\n個人有興趣係依方面發展<br />\n係咪就畢業果陣報名就得</blockquote><br />\n咁唔好做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解 其實我都考慮過好多野<br />\n個人鍾意落手落腳做，多過坐寫字樓<br />\n有朋友做緊 聽佢講我都幾有興趣</blockquote><br />\n你要考左CAD 幾科modules先<br />\nApply AELT<br />\naircraft engineering licensed trainee<br />\n你只要within個program期間, 考曬成個CAD B牌<br />\n畢業就係做Dual Function ( Inspector 收貨 出蛇）<b